{"tid":1420394,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"冷靜面對記者 記者會賽後檢討我見","createTime":"2019-08-06T04:27:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T06:17:53.000Z","uid":108040,"like":49,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"fd8edccb504a8735081a7bbdcac21a6b1390046c","tid":1420394,"uid":108040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:27:40.000Z","msg":"小弟就做PR既 以下係我個人對頭先記者會意見<br />\n想討論一下方向再出發<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家記住記者唔係你地朋友 佢地追問 問題鋒利都係正常<br />\n千萬不要屌記者<br />\n有一堆問題甚至係幫緊大家 等我地知道有咩不足</span></span><br />\n<br />\n以下係我對記者會既意見：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">建議記者會只讀聲明，發言，不設記者提問環節</span></span><br />\n<br />\n好多記者都會追問代表性，<br />\n當一提問 我地係on no grounds去答記者任何問題<br />\n3位冇組織冇身份又唔要大台<br />\n可以代答左五大訴求缺一不可<br />\n但又唔可以代答光復香港時代革命點解<br />\n咁樣已經將3位擺係一個好危險既position<br />\n因為我地自相矛盾 同時又避重就輕咁答問題<br />\n<br />\n所以記者會只可以發聲明 不宜設記者提問<br />\n<br />\n至於聲明 認受性方面<br />\n<br />\n（呢個可以再傾，以下係我暫時諗到既方法）<br />\n<br />\n聲明認受性可以以網上聯署人數確認<br />\n但一定要以email，好似大家做白宮聯署咁<br />\n記者會上就可以講<br />\n我地係作為代表，代表左XXXXXX香港市民發出既聲明......<br />\n<br />\n同時，搵香港市民發言都唔係一個記者會既好方向<br />\n冇代表性記者係唔會想理<br />\n到時呢度又搞一個 果度又搞一個<br />\n好易比政府擊破 記者都唔會再理我地<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">3位已經好叻，多謝咁趕急都搞到成件事<br />\n小弟都係希望想幫大家諗個新方向</span></span><br />\n歡迎討論 感謝<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"1a2397f4bbd941ef06e3bf1a0e4b56ee6009cbe9","tid":1420394,"uid":108040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:28:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"458dbcb1aaccb564bd04692a2461002030e0d2a4","tid":1420394,"uid":108040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:28:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9f5f778b654b9fa3697af94122e10842421b01b7","tid":1420394,"uid":108040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:29:27.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"bc8a651fbc78172d022f91d84395c2bd2fe80998","tid":1420394,"uid":1315,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:30:41.000Z","msg":"呢d先叫記者會 政府學下野啦 淺藍家母都聽到屌哂政府鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17222caef509015900f8883ec4a105e51f8b6aac","tid":1420394,"uid":108040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:31:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f6a18f1f5a04ad2b5e781b4dba219e38d7a310fc","tid":1420394,"uid":108040,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bc8a651fbc78172d022f91d84395c2bd2fe80998","tid":1420394,"uid":1315,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:30:41.000Z","msg":"呢d先叫記者會 政府學下野啦 淺藍家母都聽到屌哂政府鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:32:04.000Z","msg":"冇錯 <br />\n但如果我地揀左冇大台<br />\n就要解決認受性<br />\n同埋冇人代表到所有香港人發言呢2個問題"},{"pid":"18074b45e5b55490251f44ef000835c542ab3c4e","tid":1420394,"uid":265313,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:33:57.000Z","msg":"記者會不設發問環節，只讀聲明<br />\n邊有記者肯嚟，你做咩PR架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"831d7d1c10098abe4198795d7930ac72e49fccae","tid":1420394,"uid":108040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:34:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"933f7bcca968d8c398dfc1ee15f4b35ddbd59f20","tid":1420394,"uid":108040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"18074b45e5b55490251f44ef000835c542ab3c4e","tid":1420394,"uid":265313,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:33:57.000Z","msg":"記者會不設發問環節，只讀聲明<br />\n邊有記者肯嚟，你做咩PR架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/do